article.description: — Chris Doherty had 16 points and 10 rebounds and Northeastern held off Boston University for a 49-48 victory on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Doherty lifts Northeastern over Boston U. 49-48
article.linkText: Doherty lifts Northeastern over Boston U. 49-48
article.story: BOSTON -- — Chris Doherty had 16 points and 10 rebounds and Northeastern held off Boston University for a 49-48 victory on Tuesday night. Doherty's dunk gave Northeastern (1-2) a 49-41 lead with 2:34 remaining. Boston University scored the last seven points of the game but didn't get a final shot off before time expired. Walter Whyte had 13 points and eight rebounds for the Terriers (1-2).
